{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a7c1e900-0002-4b20-8e10-9c1d2e3f4a5b",
    "name": "Product Service - API Tests",
    "description": "Bo test API cho Product Service (pact-workshop-js/provider).\n\nCau truc: folder theo HTTP Method (GET/POST/PUT/DELETE), moi method chia 3 nhom kich ban: Happy Path, Negative, Auth Fail.\n\nAuth: middleware yeu cau header `Authorization: Bearer <ISO8601 timestamp>` voi timestamp nam trong vong 1 gio va KHONG o tuong lai. Token duoc sinh tu dong o Pre-request script cap Collection va ke thua xuong moi request.\n\nChaining: POST /products luu `createdProductId` -> PUT va DELETE Happy Path dung lai id do. Vi vay khi chay Collection Runner phai giu thu tu GET -> POST -> PUT -> DELETE.\n\nYeu cau: provider chay tai http://localhost:8080 (cd provider && npm start).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{authToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Token hop le = ISO 8601 timestamp trong vong 1 gio va khong o tuong lai.",
          "// Xem provider/middleware/auth.middleware.js: diff >= 0 && diff <= 3600",
          "// Tru 5 giay de tranh lech dong ho client/server lam diff < 0 -> 401.",
          "const token = new Date(Date.now() - 5000).toISOString();",
          "pm.environment.set('authToken', token);",
          "",
          "// Token het han dung cho nhom Auth Fail (2 gio truoc -> diff > 3600).",
          "pm.environment.set('expiredToken', new Date(Date.now() - 2 * 60 * 60 * 1000).toISOString());"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "GET",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Happy Path",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "GET /products - lay toan bo product",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "type": "text/javascript",
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Status code la 200', function () {",
                      "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                      "});",
                      "",
                      "pm.test('Body la mang khong rong', function () {",
                      "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                      "    pm.expect(body).to.be.an('array').that.is.not.empty;",
                      "});",
                      "",
                      "// LUU Y HOP DONG: chi id/type/name la BAT BUOC.",
                      "// POST /products khong yeu cau 'version' -> product tao ra co the thieu han field nay",
                      "// (JSON.stringify bo qua undefined). Vi vay khong the assert 'version' cho MOI product.",
                      "// Xem muc 'Van de da phat hien' trong AI_Audit_Report tuan 6.",
                      "pm.test('Moi product co du id, type, name', function () {",
                      "    pm.response.json().forEach(function (p) {",
                      "        pm.expect(p).to.have.property('id');",
                      "        pm.expect(p).to.have.property('type');",
                      "        pm.expect(p).to.have.property('name');",
                      "    });",
                      "});",
                      "",
                      "pm.test('Product seed (09/10/11) co field version', function () {",
                      "    pm.response.json()",
                      "        .filter(function (p) { return ['09', '10', '11'].indexOf(p.id) !== -1; })",
                      "        .forEach(function (p) { pm.expect(p).to.have.property('version'); });",
                      "});"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/products",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["products"]
                },
                "description": "Happy path: tra ve mang product seed (id 09, 10, 11)."
              },
              "response": []
            },
